lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps and Ryan Lochte cruised into the semi-finals of the 200 meters medley at the U.S. Olympic trials on Thursday to set up a potential mouth-watering showdown between the two rivals.

headline.main: Phelps and Rival Lochte on 200 IM Collision Course
